    "longBusinessSummary": "Truong Long Engineering and Auto Joint Stock Company, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the dealing and distribution of trucks and specialized vehicles under the Hino brand in Vietnam. The company offers trucks and special purpose vehicles comprising crane, canvas, dump, van, drop side, and wing trucks, as well as truck mounted cranes under the PM brand; and special purpose equipment consisting of tuck mounted cranes under the Tadano brand and dump hoists under the ShinMaywa brand. It is also involved in the manufacture of trucks and specialized vehicles; trading of machinery, equipment, spare parts, automobiles, and specialized vehicles; goods deposit agent; provision of mechanical processing, commercial, and vehicle registration services; trading houses, leasing warehouses, yards, and plants; leasing of various vehicles; design, execution, improvement, and building of road vehicles; maintenance of road vehicles; real estate brokerage and property services; repair and maintenance of vehicles; design and manufacture of upper bodies for trucks and special purpose vehicles; and insurance agent. Truong Long Engineering and Auto Joint Stock Company was founded in 1998 and is based in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
